snippet.title: Party Icons trailer | Closed Beta 1 opening in August 2024
snippet.description: Party Icons blends the whimsy and nostalgia of classic party games with the thrill of a high-stakes battle royale extraction shooter, creating an ecosystem where fun meets real rewards. Imagine the chaotic joy of classic party games in a surreal 3D art toy-like metaverse, where every match has unpredictable challenges.
